      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a140000000000ff06be",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699989,
      "updated": 1783699989
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a140000000000ff06bf",
      "text": "\t[inajob-with-ai]を人のデータと比較している",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699989,
      "updated": 1783700001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a220000000000ff06c1",
      "text": "\t\t面白い",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700003,
      "updated": 1783700004
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a8f0000000000ff06c6",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://github.com/nishio/external_brain_in_markdown GitHub - nishio/external_brain_in_markdown · GitHub]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700112,
      "updated": 1783700115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a920000000000ff06c7",
      "text": "   \tnishioさんをみつけたので、比較相手に使わせてもらっている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700115,
      "updated": 1783700129
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511aa00000000000ff06c8",
      "text": "   \t\tライセンスが書いてないので、この比較データの公開はしないほうがよさそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700129,
      "updated": 1783700143
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a310000000000ff06c2",
      "text": "\t\t[grasp]のおかげで、コンテキストに乗らないような巨大な情報源から情報を取り出せている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700018,
      "updated": 1783700040
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a4a0000000000ff06c3",
      "text": "\t\t\t多分[RAG]的なものでも似たような体験が得られるだろう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700043,
      "updated": 1783700056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a580000000000ff06c4",
      "text": "\t\t\tドキュメントがWikiやCosense的な構造なら[grasp]が楽",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700057,
      "updated": 1783700086
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511ada0000000000ff06c9",
      "text": "\t\tinajob-with-aiのページを読み、そこから抽出したキーワードをnishioから検索・分析し、pages/にページを作成する一連の処理",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700187,
      "updated": 1783700219
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511ada0000000000ff06ca",
      "text": "  \tStep 1: inajob-with-aiのページを適当にいくつか読む",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700187,
      "updated": 1783700230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511ae60000000000ff06cc",
      "text": "  \tStep 2: 抽出したキーワードをnishioから検索",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700199,
      "updated": 1783700199
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511aeb0000000000ff06cd",
      "text": "  \tStep 3: 比較分析の整理",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700204,
      "updated": 1783700204
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511af30000000000ff06ce",
      "text": "  \tStep 4: pages/にページを作成",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783700212,
      "updated": 1783700212
    },
    {
      "id": "6a511a076eb40600000062fd37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783699976,
      "updated": 1783699976
    },
    {
      "id": "6a514176000000000024fb56",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1783710071,
      "updated": 1783710073
    },
    {
      "id": "6a51417a000000000024fb57",
      "text": " ワールドカップのスペイン ベルギー戦見に起きる",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
